write all the code to achieve

00:02:20.000 --> 00:02:22.430
this kind of sign-in
and allowing your users

00:02:22.430 --> 00:02:24.810
to share their identity
with your server.

00:02:24.810 --> 00:02:26.050
I'm Laurence Moroney.

00:02:26.050 --> 00:02:28.140
And you're going to
go build better apps.

